<h1>Create a new Owner</h1> #creating new ownerwith a field of owners name

<form action="/owners" method="POST">
  <label>Name:</label>

  <br>

  <input type="text" name="owner[name]">

  <h3>Existing Pets</h3> #owner with exisiting pets. Here is a checked box
  <% @pets.each do |pet| %>
    <input type="checkbox" name="owner[pet_ids][]" id="<%= pet.id %>" value="<%= pet.id %>"><%= pet.name %><br>
  <% end %>
  <br>

  <input type="submit" value="Create Owner">
</form>
